Global Water Purification Equipment for Dialysis Market Insights
Water Purification Equipment for Dialysis Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Water Purification Equipment for Dialysis Market Overview
The global market for water purification equipment used in dialysis procedures was valued at approximately USD 770.45 million in 2024. This market is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.95% from 2024 to 2030, reaching an estimated value of USD 1.2 billion by 2030. The market is segmented by type into single-stage and two-stage systems, with single-stage systems accounting for a larger share due to their cost-effectiveness and efficiency. Applications are primarily in hospitals and hemodialysis centers, which together constitute the majority of the market share. Geographically, North America leads the market, followed by Europe and the Asia-Pacific region.

